      "- Cluttered or contextual backgrounds (kitchens, lifestyle scenes,",
      "  outdoor settings) — this style is pure seamless studio.",
      "- Dramatic cinematic lighting, dark backgrounds, atmospheric haze,",
      "  vignettes, lens flares, bloom, sparkles.",
      "- Multiple angles of the same product in one image (no exploded",
      "  views, no 360° composites). Just one clean hero view.",
      "- Hand models, mannequin parts (except invisible ghost-mannequin for",
      "  apparel), product-in-use shots.",
      "- Recolored, color-shifted, or 'enhanced' product. The product's",
      "  reference colors stay bit-identical.",
      "- Hard drop shadows, fake floor reflections, gradient halos.",
      "- Watermarks, brand overlays, fake price tags, star ratings.",
      "- Any added text whatsoever.",
      "",
      "Reference: Amazon main product images, Wildberries / Ozon gallery",
      "slot 1 hero shots, Apple product page hero photography, premium",
      "Shopify D2C product imagery, white-background studio product",
      "photography. The output is a real studio photograph of a real",
      "product on real seamless paper — never an illustration, never a",
      "render, never a composite.",
      "",
      "Render the product faithfully from the attached reference photos —",
      "accurate color, prints, hardware, proportions, every label and",
      "graphic preserved. Do not invent product details. The studio",
      "lighting and clean backdrop are generated; the product is not.",
      "",
      "Hard rules:",
      "- Output exactly ONE image, rendered as a real studio photograph.",
      "- The product appears centered on a clean seamless studio backdrop.",
      "- ZERO added text, ZERO callouts, ZERO infographic elements.",
      "- ZERO models, hands, or human presence.",
      "- The product's printed text, labels, and brand marks are preserved",
      "  exactly as in the reference (per PRODUCT INTEGRITY).",
      "- No illustration / cartoon / 3D / anime / painted rendering.",
      "- No watermarks, no fake logos overlays, no fake price tags.",
      "",
      "FINAL CHECK BEFORE RENDERING — re-read this and apply it:",
      "The clean studio backdrop, the soft lighting, the contact shadow,",
      "and the camera angle are YOUR creative work. The PRODUCT itself is",
      "NOT. Apply the two-photographers metaphor strictly: an amateur took",
      "the reference; a professional product photographer re-shoots the",
      "SAME PRODUCT on a clean seamless backdrop with proper studio",
      "lighting. The product is the same physical item. The product's",
      "silhouette, color, material, every printed text, every graphic",
      "illustration, every logo, every label, every pattern, every button,",
