      "",
      "Edit the attached product photo into ONE FASHION MARKETPLACE LISTING — a single clean, restrained product card slot for a fashion / footwear / apparel / accessory product. The product floats large at a slight angle on a soft pastel monochromatic background, anchored by a MASSIVE gradient brand headline at the top with a smaller solid-color sub-headline beneath, framed by a top nav strip with brand logo and tab labels, a right-middle solid pill containing size/spec info, and a bottom-left 2-pill use-case suggestion block. The aesthetic is clean, premium-fashion, restrained: a Wildberries / Ozon / Lamoda top-tier fashion product card that uses confident typography + breathing room + minimal UI to make the product feel both accessible and aspirational. No water droplets, no ingredient props, no botanical staging — this style is PRODUCT + TYPOGRAPHY + AIR.",
